query:
UPDATE custom_scenarios
            SET title = $2,
                description = $3,
                discipline = $4,
                mode = $5,
                kickoff_prompt = $6,
                passing_score = $7,
                supplemental_info = $8,
                behavior = $9,
                product = $10,
                evaluation_criteria = $11,
                missions = $12
            WHERE id = $1
